        "code_body": "class Program   \n{ static int SumVals() { int val1 $= 2$ int val2 $= 3$ int sum $\\equiv$ val1\\*val2; return sum; } static void Main(string( args) { Console.WriteLine(\"Summed Values $=$ {sum}\"); Console. ReadKey(); } ",
